Exception When raised <code>SchemaParseError</code> Input schema format unrecognised or file unreadable <code>ValidationRetryError</code> Both validation attempts fail in <code>safe_mode</code>; carries <code>.raw</code> and <code>.validation_errors</code> <code>PolicyGenerationError</code> LLM returns empty/non-JSON response; <code>compile=True</code> with unavailable compiler; malformed <code>input</code> dict <pre><code>from rbacx.ai import AIPolicy, ValidationRetryError, PolicyGenerationError

try:
    result = await ai.from_schema("openapi.json")
except ValidationRetryError as e:
    print("Failed after two attempts:")
    for err in e.validation_errors:
        print(f"  {err}")
    print("Last raw output:", e.raw)
except PolicyGenerationError as e:
    print("Generation error:", e)
    if e.cause:
        print("Caused by:", e.cause)
</code></pre>
